{"tid":783572,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]半年10萬HKD外匯EA倉,你問我唔答","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T02:43:35.000Z","uid":36289,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8976e44e1c2d82a99371d96b9aaf78453e1f9cd1","tid":783572,"uid":36289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"半martingale，志在分享，不含教學<br />\n<br />\n以前覺得martingale都係搵笨,遲早一定爆<br />\n一直都係用人手trade果套方法黎寫ea,zigzag curve 向上都ok靚<br />\ne個係幫朋友炒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/225752_01effdac6062831623d62c08febfb1df.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F225752_01effdac6062831623d62c08febfb1df.PNG&h=b3850662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但朋友話幾寧願平穩d慢慢上,個個月都out金洗都唔想有大上大落<br />\n我都覺得係,就算dd有幾細都好都想整走佢,連大上都唔想有,因為有大上其實意味住有大落風險<br />\n例如tp 10pips, sl自然都係咁上下,5-20pips<br />\n但tp 400pips冇可能set sl做20pips咁短線,chok一下就冇左<br />\n所以想整個直線curve,寧願賺少d都想平穩d<br />\n如果本大,自然想安全多過發達,賺10%都不得了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以開始研究martingale,經過無數次仆街之後...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183007_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183007_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG&h=fb5e572f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183007_ed15309095e612491ee3f1f7bd27241b.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183007_ed15309095e612491ee3f1f7bd27241b.PNG&h=a65e5aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183007_678c31e8b371bddc10ee6439d9839e84.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183007_678c31e8b371bddc10ee6439d9839e84.PNG&h=f92c5607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183007_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183007_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG&h=7f34f4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183007_4517285d30d12c978510261c986ec773.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183007_4517285d30d12c978510261c986ec773.PNG&h=3c0074d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183007_f4cab5d793d627287b274cd8976ef051.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183007_f4cab5d793d627287b274cd8976ef051.PNG&h=4a91ec58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183008_cd1ae5fd93fd3d6d1289c3244bd2405e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183008_cd1ae5fd93fd3d6d1289c3244bd2405e.PNG&h=5c55b9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183008_6d65fb96b7c32c37bade4d8efc722697.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183008_6d65fb96b7c32c37bade4d8efc722697.PNG&h=f08aa5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/183008_a9f6262884ffa5617d8922a24e28151f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F183008_a9f6262884ffa5617d8922a24e28151f.PNG&h=da200dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結 :<br />\n1, 如果想用chok一個完美數值出黎, 應該冇可能。例如每相距n pips就加m倍lot size<br />\n2. martingale只係講點加倉,冇講點入市,如果想是但開個倉之後martingale加倉,加到賺,應該一樣冇可能<br />\n3. ea搵岩方向+入市位,再用martingale某n m加倉, backtest竟然冇試過爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入市方向本身舊ea都已經有7成,如果咁唔好彩方向錯左先用martingale<br />\n所以未試加多過5個倉(backtest同真倉都係,2者基本上result一樣,只係有時spread差1.x pips, 始終backtest spread資料有不足)<br />\n試過用其他入市方法都一樣差唔多,如果本身命中率有7成都應該好安全<br />\n<br />\ne個account會life到世界末日,或者爆倉<br />\n但今個月開始會set大個lot size,始終回報真係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果靠e個開飯好快訓街"},{"pid":"c5e75340da5c83a8cc7f821f354b7981fe8e8aa6","tid":783572,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0796a62b00bd06eac861ed051e4ae45326aa27e8","tid":783572,"uid":68118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"水坑巴，我偶像 <br />\n難得出po 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b160aa25ccb007c6d9541c549937bc44d54cc4f1","tid":783572,"uid":185265,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:58:48.000Z","msg":"賭場用 martingle 就死硬，因為有封頂，forex就只要本大或可接受慢升，九成九九贏，但一輸就真係好似中左負數六合彩咁，但有幾多人會中六合彩呢？<br />\n<br />\n你呢個 use case 幾有趣，俾我會加個 half kelly."},{"pid":"b683d9aad9e35ab809b0f916ec4709df2eb84bd1","tid":783572,"uid":35095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm"},{"pid":"01c3b3e61e0af978feacb53fc332e015632fcfeb","tid":783572,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"請問ea是咩？<br />\n<br />\n加注是否上一注嘅double?"},{"pid":"7994052d3f442012647b39dbe66fee0af26f7f06","tid":783572,"uid":185265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01c3b3e61e0af978feacb53fc332e015632fcfeb","tid":783572,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"請問ea是咩？<br />\n<br />\n加注是否上一注嘅double?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T20:00:43.000Z","msg":"metatrader 用來定義 trading strategy 的一種檔案，全名叫 Expert Advisor,  類似 C program 嘅 syntax.  有興趣可